    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
    "body" : "<p>Check this: <a href=\"http://download.oracle.com/javase/1.5.0/docs/api/java/lang/System.html#currentTimeMillis%28%29\" rel=\"noreferrer\">System.currentTimeMillis</a>.</p>\n\n<p>With this you can calculate the time of your method by doing:</p>\n\n<pre><code>long start = System.currentTimeMillis();\nclass.method();\nlong time = System.currentTimeMillis() - start;\n</code></pre>\n"
  }, {
